INSTALL
*******

RPM based linux distribution
----------------------------
The simplest way to install this package is by installing provided RPM
package. RPM package can be downloaded from:

https://github.com/adhisimon/bijinclock/downloads

Non RPM based linux distribution
--------------------------------
For non RPM based linux distribution, the simplest way to install this
package is:

  1. `cd' to the directory containing the package's source code.

  2. Type `make install' to install the programs and any data files and
     documentation.

  3. You can remove the program binaries and object files from the
     source code directory by typing `make clean'.

  4. You can uninstall package by running `make uninstall'.

Developmental source code
-------------------------
You can get last developmental (unstable) version using git command:

git clone git://github.com/adhisimon/bijinclock.git



